* [[英國|英國]][[伯明翰|伯明翰]]第四屆歐洲銅管與敲擊樂器國際大賽木琴冠軍及最佳表演大獎<ref name=":1">{{cite web|title=林金丞浪漫木琴前進卡內基|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20180326000105-260301?chdtv|accessdate=2018-03-26|archiveurl=https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20180326000105-260301?chdtv|archivedate=2021-02-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>

